# Alicia Bus Architecture - Development MQTT Access Control List
# Simplified ACL for development and testing

# Allow all access for development
# In production, use the full acl file with proper restrictions

# Admin user for management and debugging
user admin
topic readwrite alicia/#
topic readwrite $SYS/#

# Allow anonymous access for development
topic readwrite alicia/#

# Deny all other access (this won't apply in development mode)
topic deny alicia/#
